# Proxy API calls to the backend on Render so the browser stays same-origin
# (keeps the httpOnly auth cookie first-party). MUST be above the SPA catch-all,
# because Netlify processes _redirects top-to-bottom and first match wins.
/api/*  https://scribble-t478.onrender.com/api/:splat  200

# SPA fallback: serve index.html for any other route (React Router deep links).
/*  /index.html  200
